_sText:
Surf_Greatriver but with a few fixes to make it neater and add in a few things to make the map better, I do not take credit for the creation of the map, but i do take credit for this upload and all the editing done by me.

Some of the things changed/edited:
- Completely redone textures
- Remade surf ramps (less glitchy)
- Fixed a lot of failures
- Cleaned everything up
- Added secrets (x3) ... (hidden trail smoke nade, awp and ladder to the roof of top)..
- Lot's more!

(Download file compressed with winrar, google for the latest version)
